@@TJvImageSplit
Description:
This component splits images into R/G/B or H/S/V or monochrome

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvImageSplit.GetBBitmap@TBitmap
Description:
This will return a bitmap with only the blue component of the source bitmap

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvImageSplit.GetGBitmap@TBitmap
Description:
This will return a bitmap with only the green component of the source bitmap

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvImageSplit.GetHueBitmap@TBitmap
Description:
This will return a bitmap with only the hue of the source bitmap

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvImageSplit.GetMonochromeBitmap@TBitmap
Description:
This will return a monochrome bitmap

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvImageSplit.GetRBitmap@TBitmap
Description:
This will return a bitmap with only the red component of the source bitmap

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvImageSplit.GetSaturationBitmap@TBitmap
Description:
This will return a bitmap with only the saturation of the source bitmap

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvImageSplit.GetValueBitmap@TBitmap
Description:
This will return a bitmap with only the Value of the source bitmap

